{"tid":453142,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"雞蛋六隻 糖兩茶匙 再加d橙皮 係煮緊d咩嘢食?","createTime":"2017-10-31T02:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T07:52:06.000Z","uid":19563,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"12fdafd72d23b73cbb34b0f1147290e257e56efc","tid":453142,"uid":19563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:20:13.000Z","msg":"其實係乜L嘢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2383e124b096be23fe769c29d0751cc9684be9bb","tid":453142,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"甜品"},{"pid":"f52c8446d5cdd66fec14aebf411e636322dc5f4c","tid":453142,"uid":103543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"唔係梳乎里就係焦糖燉蛋啦"},{"pid":"c217ba5165a81b5546f92df928ed2cf67b1fc60d","tid":453142,"uid":29684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:34:00.000Z","msg":"轉身射個3分波先!"},{"pid":"737669dcdfdd553e5a1d2c45c98563e726649c67","tid":453142,"uid":101804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔係個個節目都岩小朋友自己收睇"},{"pid":"8ddadfb366911c5866edd112de2877841dd776a2","tid":453142,"uid":152376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"橙皮燉蛋"},{"pid":"89733c5a4bc1c2eeaededdfd2fa932a99069abb2","tid":453142,"uid":121393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"咖哩"},{"pid":"d9e044f2546b115457caa2fc379355eb4744a449","tid":453142,"uid":62837,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"蛋糕呀<br />\n要有水果味 不嬲落皮"},{"pid":"64693ade37379843b9d15cbcbe461e9b6725d480","tid":453142,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛋糕呀<br />\n要有水果味 不嬲落皮</blockquote><br />\nD皮係蛋糕入面?"},{"pid":"6c8f4c7d058573002eb3e889314fab25b90fae97","tid":453142,"uid":93394,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蛋糕呀<br />\n要有水果味 不嬲落皮</blockquote><br />\nD皮係蛋糕入面?</blockquote><br />\n未食過蛋糕？"},{"pid":"3213389aa99e00749b557a006004b3861cf0bfa5","tid":453142,"uid":24641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"你唔你諗住成塊放落去呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5e790ea9eb8887dd6d0a4455182957af5e2824","tid":453142,"uid":24989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"橙皮蛋糕"},{"pid":"7d9398fdad38ea48fba7e02786cc212730812e72","tid":453142,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"駁嘴？"},{"pid":"a907e19ac7631fe3b9b4d2a2016d1cce9ca610ed","tid":453142,"uid":32028,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:22:08.000Z","msg":"清香鮮橙蒸蛋<br />\n材料：橙(1隻)、雞蛋(2隻) 調料：白糖(1湯匙)<br />\n做法：<br />\n1、鮮橙洗凈拭乾水，放在砧板上用手掌輕揉5分鐘。<br />\n2、將鮮橙切成兩半，掏出橙肉，橙皮做成盛器。<br />\n3、將橙肉放入榨汁機內打成橙汁，濾去果肉渣。<br />\n4、雞蛋打入碗內，加入1湯匙細砂糖，打散成蛋液，與橙汁混合均勻。<br />\n5、分別將蛋液倒入兩隻橙皮中，倒至八分滿便可。<br />\n6、將橙皮蛋液放入盤中，蓋上一層保鮮膜待用。<br />\n7、燒開鍋內的水，放入橙皮蛋液，加蓋以中火隔水清蒸10分鐘。<br />\n8、取出蒸好的鮮橙蒸蛋，撕去保鮮膜，即可上桌。"},{"pid":"73567664d7622a0b95234e8e9456904cded24ec9","tid":453142,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"唔係班戟咩？"},{"pid":"d552050708dc7181bf848e1c160ba0ff21fd4a31","tid":453142,"uid":18117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"得果兩茶匙咁少糖整乜春野蛋糕呀"},{"pid":"0d089b4e86ebd92d55d2257cac8230d96daa7a2d","tid":453142,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42d6930983fa2f15cd51179d99d312885a275ae6","tid":453142,"uid":90787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得果兩茶匙咁少糖整乜春野蛋糕呀</blockquote><br />\n仲要6隻雞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔准駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話係蛋糕就係蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0326be49284bdc4c38028acd0905ffa7623683","tid":453142,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係梳乎里就係焦糖燉蛋啦</blockquote><br />\n之前馬田話過呢個食譜如果係梳乎里<br />\n好似話會好漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3f4f9822610169ffbf73e16f87d4beb28fd91c","tid":453142,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"SoyJoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e63677e5f5f39f4f039908d55cc87087d1a4aa","tid":453142,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清香鮮橙蒸蛋<br />\n材料：橙(1隻)、雞蛋(2隻) 調料：白糖(1湯匙)<br />\n做法：<br />\n1、鮮橙洗凈拭乾水，放在砧板上用手掌輕揉5分鐘。<br />\n2、將鮮橙切成兩半，掏出橙肉，橙皮做成盛器。<br />\n3、將橙肉放入榨汁機內打成橙汁，濾去果肉渣。<br />\n4、雞蛋打入碗內，加入1湯匙細砂糖，打散成蛋液，與橙汁混合均勻。<br />\n5、分別將蛋液倒入兩隻橙皮中，倒至八分滿便可。<br />\n6、將橙皮蛋液放入盤中，蓋上一層保鮮膜待用。<br />\n7、燒開鍋內的水，放入橙皮蛋液，加蓋以中火隔水清蒸10分鐘。<br />\n8、取出蒸好的鮮橙蒸蛋，撕去保鮮膜，即可上桌。</blockquote><br />\n幽默大師寫架個食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e07733e7afef8f6b3bf1f1e6c02df8d5560c34c","tid":453142,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係梳乎里就係焦糖燉蛋啦</blockquote><br />\n之前馬田話過呢個食譜如果係梳乎里<br />\n好似話會好漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6隻蛋整梳乎里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130fbe57b02fc4ea0aee90582df56533b578516e","tid":453142,"uid":121409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係梳乎里就係焦糖燉蛋啦</blockquote><br />\n之前馬田話過呢個食譜如果係梳乎里<br />\n好似話會好漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6隻蛋整梳乎里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n糖得兩茶匙整甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc663a52e5ec2cb31c972ae4121bea2e39b569d","tid":453142,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"橙皮蒸蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6fb800bbd4f73251f44c9f1d6af384ac7d4a56","tid":453142,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蒸水蛋蒸6隻？仲要加糖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點睇都似甜品"}]}